<% if(title){ %>
<h1><%= title %></h1>
<% } else { %>
<h1>Oops! Something Went Wrong</h1>
<% } %>

<div class="error-container">
  <div class="error-content">
    <div class="error-icon">🚗💨</div>
    <h2>Our servers just took an unexpected detour!</h2>
    
    <div class="error-message">
      <p><strong>Error Details:</strong></p>
      <div class="message-box">
        <%- message %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="error-humor">
      <p>Don't worry, our mechanics are already under the hood trying to fix this issue. 
         In the meantime, why not check out our amazing selection of vehicles?</p>
      
      <div class="error-suggestions">
        <h3>While you wait, you could:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>🏠 <a href="/">Return to our homepage</a></li>
          <li>🚗 <a href="/inv">Browse our inventory</a></li>
          <li>☕ Grab a coffee and try again in a few minutes</li>
          <li>🎵 Listen to some Back to the Future soundtrack</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="error-quote">
      <blockquote>
        <p>"Roads? Where we're going, we don't need roads... but we do need working servers!"</p>
        <cite>- Doc Brown (probably)</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.error-container {
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 2rem auto;
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

.error-icon {
  font-size: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.error-content h2 {
  color: #d32f2f;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.message-box {
  background-color: #f5f5f5;
  border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;
  padding: 1rem;
  margin: 1rem 0;
  text-align: left;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-family: monospace;
}

.error-humor {
  margin: 2rem 0;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  background-color: #e3f2fd;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.error-suggestions ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.error-suggestions li {
  margin: 0.5rem 0;
  padding: 0.5rem;
}

.error-suggestions a {
  color: #1976d2;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.error-suggestions a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

.error-quote {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  padding: 1rem;
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
}

.error-quote cite {
  display: block;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #666;
}
</style> 